dct_title_s: Mapa geologico de Honduras. Santa Cruz de Yojoa, hoja 2660 IV G
dct_description_sm: Honduras. Instituto Geografico Nacional. United States. Peace Corps. North Decimal Degree 15.000000. South Decimal Degree 14.8333. East Decimal Degree -87.7500. West Decimal Degree -88.0000. Alternate title: Mapa geologico Santa Cruz de Yojoa, Honduras, C. A. In upper margin: Geologia Honduras 1:50,000. Universal transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by 20 m. contour interval and spot heights.
